text: Curt Steuernagel (1886 - 30 July 1918) was a German gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1886 births Category:1918 deaths Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
